# Spotify "now playing" easter egg — optional.
# Without these, the terminal falls back to a static WAIT FOR U card.
#
# Setup:
# 1. Create an app at https://developer.spotify.com/dashboard
#    (redirect URI: http://localhost:3000/callback)
# 2. Get a refresh token with scopes:
#    user-read-currently-playing user-read-recently-played
#    Easiest path: https://accounts.spotify.com/authorize?client_id=YOUR_ID&response_type=code&redirect_uri=http://localhost:3000/callback&scope=user-read-currently-playing%20user-read-recently-played
#    then exchange the code for a refresh_token via the token endpoint.
# 3. Copy this file to .env.local and fill in. Add the same vars in Vercel.

SPOTIFY_CLIENT_ID=
SPOTIFY_CLIENT_SECRET=
SPOTIFY_REFRESH_TOKEN=
